title: GolfTEC Huntington Beach- Client Appreciation Night
desc: Join us at GolfTEC Huntington Beach on?12/10/15 for our Callaway Client Appreciation Night. Feel free to bring friends and family to participate in the Guess Your Drive Distance?and Closest-to-the-Pin contests for prizes. There will be complimentary BBQ?and beverage served throughout the event.?This event is open to GolfTEC Students, friends and family. Don't miss out on this special event! We look forward to seeing you there!
